Description: Triggers a Star Burst dealing 14872 Damage when Energy Shield breaks or fills
When damaged, gain +15% Elemental Resistance and +50% Resistance to the last damage type received for 5s
On kill, 50% chance to spawn an Ammo Booster and instantly refill Gun Ammo
On Melee Hit, consume an Armor Segment to gain +100% Melee Damage. When Armor Shield is 0, gain +50% Melee Damage
On Armor Segment break, grants 753 Overshield
Spawns a Shield Boi when the last Armor Segment breaks
While equipped, gain +7436 Max Health, regenerate +372 Health/s, and reduce Damage Taken by 33%

When damaged, gain a stack of Determination. Each stack reduces Damage Taken by 2%, max 25 stacks. When Energy Shield breaks, release a Star Burst dealing 7436 Damage, increased by +20% per stack of Determination
Toggle via Ground Slam. When active, continuously drains Shield to gain +40% Bonus Shock Damage, but incoming Damage bypasses Shield
Periodically shocks nearby enemies while Energy Shield is not full
When Energy Shield is active, damaged enemies have a 12% chance to drop Overshield. While you have Overshield, gain +25% Shock Damage
When Energy Shield breaks, trigger a Star Burst on 3 enemies dealing 5577 Damage
Gain 2 seconds of Damage Immunity when an Armor Segment breaks
While equipped, revive faster in Fight For Your Life. Automatically gain a Second Wind when FFYL time expires (300s cooldown)
Gain Overshield when Energy Shield fills. When Energy Shield is full, gain +25% Fire Rate, +25% Movement Speed, and regenerate 1 Ammo/s
On kill, spawn Missiles that home in on nearby enemies, dealing 7436 Damage each
Immediately lose an Armor Segment when Armor Shield becomes full
